Class SphericalMercatorCoordSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.CoordSystem
      • com.mousebird.maply.SphericalMercatorCoordSystem

  • public class SphericalMercatorCoordSystem
extends CoordSystem
    A wrapper around Maply's spherical mercator coordinate system implementation. Spherical mercator is the mostly commonly used coordinate system in tile based implementations on the web.
